{"word":"μέτασσαι","slug":"μέτασσαι","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n66942\" key=\"me/tassai\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">μέτασσαι</orth>, <gen lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gen\">αἱ</gen>, <sense id=\"n66942.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <xr opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"xr\"> <lbl opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"lbl\">=</lbl> <ref targOrder=\"U\" lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"ref\">μεταγενεῖς</ref></xr>, of lambs, <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">χωρὶς μὲν πρόγονοι, χωρὶς δὲ μέτασσαι, χωρὶς δ᾽ αὖθ᾽ ἕρσαι</foreign>, i.e. the early-born, <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">those born later</tr_>, and the freshlings or late-born, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:9:221\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Od.\">Od.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">9.221</biblScope> </bibl>:—also neut. <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">τὰ</foreign> </sense> </entryFree>"}]}